<lb ed="I" n="0034b03" type="honorific"/>之碑</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0034c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0034c0101">夫玄猷沖<note n="0034001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB06418"/>＝容【史】</note><note n="0034001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB06418"/>【佛拓】，容【史】</note><app n="0034001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">容</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB06418"/></rdg></app>。而繁□塵其暉。冥淵澄鏡。而綺波式其澗。□□□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c02" type="honorific"/>使三有紛離。六塵<note n="0034002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30411"/>＝囂【史】</note><note n="0034002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30411"/>【佛拓】，囂【史】</note><app n="0034002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">囂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30411"/></rdg></app>翳。輪迴幽塗。迷趣靡返者也。是以至覺垂悲。拯彼沉溺。闡<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">三</unclear>□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c03" type="honorific"/>火宅。秉湛一之維則。騰道於妙境。叵夕暉<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">慧</unclear>日之旦。大千矚常樂之□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">慈</unclear>風□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c04" type="honorific"/>若不遷之訓。周誨於昏明。万化無虧之範。永播於幽顯。通塞歸乎有緣。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">行</unclear>藏<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">盛</unclear>□□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c05" type="honorific"/>皇帝陛下。聖契潛通。應期纂曆。道氣籠三才之經。至德蓋五常之緯。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">啟</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">唐</unclear>□□魏□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c06" type="honorific"/>五教遐融。禮風遠<note n="0034003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">剬＝制【史】</note><note n="0034003" resp="ihp" type="mod">剬【佛拓】，制【史】</note><app n="0034003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">制</lem><rdg wit="【原】">剬</rdg></app>。慈導開章。真宗顯誥。戒綱羈乎有心。政<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">觀</unclear>變乎□□。彼<note n="0034004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">堓＝岸【史】</note><note n="0034004" resp="ihp" type="mod">堓【佛拓】，岸【史】</note><app n="0034004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">岸</lem><rdg wit="【原】">堓</rdg></app>之．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c07" type="honorific"/>於茲將濟矣。自惟鴻源帝鄉。庇鄰雲液。議蹤翼<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">親</unclear>。論疇懿胕。榮要山河。連基齊晉。遂得．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c08" type="honorific"/>金於雲階。班爵五等。垂玉於丹墀。內備幃幄。外委霜□。專節戎場。闢土之效未申。耀威．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c09" type="honorific"/>志靡建。豈謂乾蔭雲敷。皇澤雨灑。沖旨徧加。春華交暎。<note n="0034005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30412"/>＝勢【史】</note><note n="0034005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30412"/>【佛拓】，勢【史】</note><app n="0034005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勢</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30412"/></rdg></app>均兩嶽。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">曜</unclear>軒三蕃。列土□□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c10" type="honorific"/>崇海量。介焉罔酬。遂尋案經教。追訪法圖。冥福起於顯誓。鴻報發於涓心。悟尋訓旨。建．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c11" type="honorific"/>厥涇陽。簡茲名埠。重巒煙蔚。景氣之初交。川流泱瀁。鮮榮之後暢。飛峭合霄。玄崖吐液。．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c12" type="honorific"/>峙冥造之形。風水蕭散。嗂韻之<app type="star" corresp="#0034005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勢</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30412"/></rdg></app>。命匠呈奇。競工開剖。積節移年。營<note n="0034006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30414"/>＝構【史】</note><note n="0034006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30414"/>【佛拓】，構【史】</note><app n="0034006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">構</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30414"/></rdg></app>乃就。圖雙林之遺．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c13" type="honorific"/>於玄堂。<note n="0034007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𩑬＝規【史】</note><note n="0034007" resp="ihp" type="mod">𩑬【佛拓】，規【史】</note><app n="0034007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">規</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩑬</rdg></app>住聖之鴻質。則巍嶷於<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">虛</unclear>室。群像垂霄<app type="star" corresp="#0034001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">容</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB06418"/></rdg></app>之朗。眾<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">影</unclear>表朱光之鮮。暉暉焉。若□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c14" type="honorific"/>饘。岌岌焉。如踊出之應法機。又<app type="star" corresp="#0034006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">構</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30414"/></rdg></app>以房館。建之堂閣。藻潔渟津。蔭□殊例。靜宇禪區。眾□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c15" type="honorific"/>窮微之<note n="0034008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30416"/>＝僧【史】</note><note n="0034008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30416"/>【佛拓】，僧【史】</note><app n="0034008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">僧</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30416"/></rdg></app>近。跧通寂之儁蹠。塵誠裨乎治端。豪績瑍乎不朽。刊銘寺庭。遂興頌曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0034c16" type="honorific"/>攸攸冥造。寥寥太虛。動以應有。靜以照无。穹經垂像。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">淳</unclear>化亦敷。囂□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">紛</unclear>□。道隱昏塗。造□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c17" type="honorific"/>四色。俗流競波。愛根爭殖。迴住幽衢。沈淪邪或。聖覺匪運。真圖<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">詎</unclear>測。至哉大覺。持暢靈姿。．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c18" type="honorific"/>廓茲聖維。大千被化。幽境蒙暉。潛神吐曜。應我皇機。聖皇玄感。協<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">揚</unclear>治猷。道液垂津。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">冥</unclear>被．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c19" type="honorific"/>九區。慧鏡長<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">幽</unclear>。三乘既駕。六<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">塵</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">斯</unclear>流。<note n="0034009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">湌＝餐【史】</note><note n="0034009" resp="ihp" type="mod">湌【佛拓】，餐【史】</note><app n="0034009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">餐</lem><rdg wit="【原】">湌</rdg></app>沐法膏。澡心道津。鴻源流<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">衍</unclear>。是近是親。均感遐舊。．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c20" type="honorific"/><note n="0034010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30415"/>＝痛【史】</note><note n="0034010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30415"/>【佛拓】，痛【史】</note><app n="0034010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">痛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30415"/></rdg></app>躬罔報。建斯嘉因。重阿疊巖。蔚暎陽川。邃戶飛<note n="0034011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">窓＝窗【史】</note><note n="0034011" resp="ihp" type="mod">窓【佛拓】，窗【史】</note><app n="0034011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">窗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">窓</rdg></app>。翠錯<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">暉</unclear>妍。雙<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">林</unclear>運矣。遺儀更鮮。□□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0034c21" type="honorific"/>永證。
<lb ed="I" n="0034c22" type="honorific"/>一　大魏永平三年歲在庚寅四月壬寅朔十四日乙卯。使持節都督涇州諸軍事平西<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">將</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">軍</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0034c23" type="honorific"/>　　涇□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">州</unclear>刺史安武縣開國男<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">奚</unclear>康生造</p>
